Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.98,0:01:36.55,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Gin-san? What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:38.65,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,How could you screw up the \Nend of the opening sequence?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.65,0:01:39.95,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:41.36,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,There's bound to be a mishap when
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:43.25,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,you do the same thing 23 times in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.25,0:01:46.24,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the opening \Nwas reused every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.24,0:01:48.01,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't supposed to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.01,0:01:50.93,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too embarrassed to show my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:54.11,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to do this next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:54.86,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:55.85,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:57.38,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Say, since this is so embarrassing,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:01:59.01,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,can we cut to commercial?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:01.43,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Recycling Shop\NEarth Defense Force
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:02.02,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:03.43,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:08.23,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Doraemon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:04.96,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,A VHS player.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.96,0:02:05.95,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Buy it off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:08.23,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,There's a tape stuck inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:11.64,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It comes with a video tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:16.21,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Nobody buys or sells \NVHS players these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:18.20,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Man, don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:22.24,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It says Doraemon on the \Ntape, but it's not Doraemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:26.60,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,There's no flying or \Nfour-dimensional pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:30.52,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Just a nasty pocket with a whacked Gian.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:32.90,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Your head is whacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:35.46,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I can't leave this \Nsitting around at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:37.06,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Gian is sticking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:38.58,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just recycle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:42.34,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to buy it, I'm \Nwilling to trade it in for something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:43.61,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Like a DVD.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:46.97,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to play straw \Nmillionaire, go somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.89,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I do have a Blu-ray player.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:53.50,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:57.76,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that I have a Blu-ray \Nplayer that I'll trade for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:02:59.40,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Blu-rays are better than DVDs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:03.95,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You can see the pores \Nin Shizuka-chan's skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:08.08,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,You can see Shizuka-chan like \Nyou've never seen her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:10.32,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Are you sure about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:11.37,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.61,0:03:13.55,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:17.81,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,There's a Gian recital \Ngoing on here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:24.89,On Screen,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,Blue and Red Ecstasy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:27.39,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What's that, Gin-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:30.89,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,B-Blu-ray...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:32.89,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Blu-ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:35.36,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have such an \Nexpensive machine here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:37.48,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I straw millionaire'd myself a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:39.89,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,broken Blu-ray player out \Nof a broken VHS player.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:42.91,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, so you traded trash for trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:46.64,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But it's like a tissue used \Nto wipe this dumb girl's nose
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:49.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,versus a tissue used to \Nwipe Otsuu-chan's lipstick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:51.23,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The latter wouldn't be a tissue anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:52.25,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a holy shroud.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:55.92,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how about I stuff my \Nshroud down your throat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:59.24,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,But this thing is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could get \Nthis disc out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:04.89,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It won't even budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:07.33,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,What's on that disc anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.58,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:11.14,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The former owner jammed it in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:14.89,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You can't pull or push it, but it spins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:16.58,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,There's something written on the disc.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:23.03,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The Cursed Blu-ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:24.32,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:25.09,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:28.08,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of cursed video tapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.66,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The ones where you die \Nif you watch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:32.92,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:36.35,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost comes out of \Nthe TV and kills you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:37.84,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:42.30,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never heard of \Na cursed Blu-ray before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:44.58,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Well, video tapes are too dated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:47.85,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Ghosts also have to \Nkeep up with the times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:50.27,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This isn't funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:53.25,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see a \Nhigh-definition ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:54.09,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:55.14,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna return this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:56.40,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Gin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.16,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't unplug it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:05.16,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I put it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:06.30,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:08.21,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Let's watch it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:10.11,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you babbling about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:11.68,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:13.45,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably just a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.48,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That cursed video tape was just a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.67,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Just turn the TV off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:17.99,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:20.00,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Turn around then, Gin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.67,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn the volume down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.18,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:29.08,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The remote isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:30.02,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:31.38,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:32.98,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:35.68,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I can see something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:39.50,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't that a well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:40.84,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This is, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:42.21,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,where that person lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:44.69,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This is really bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:47.89,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,There it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:48.94,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It was all true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:50.58,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We're so screwed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:55.22,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Uh oh, it's going to jump out \Nof the TV and kill us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:55.95,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Shinpachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.08,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Grab a pot lid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:57.58,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.06,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:00.50,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how it works!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:03.61,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-chan, it's coming closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:05.51,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy it! Destroy the TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:08.89,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Gin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:09.76,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.98,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:20.07,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kotatsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:20.85,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Kotatsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:22.06,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:23.51,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Is that some kind of deadly curse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.12,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! She's leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:27.21,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it, but she's \Ngoing back to the well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:28.31,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Did I turn it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:30.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! She just said, "Did I turn it off"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:31.81,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So she meant kotatsu as \Nin the heated table?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:34.73,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,She went back to make \Nsure she turned it off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:37.77,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, what kind of ghost would \Ngo back to check on a kotatsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:39.77,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And is there a kotatsu down there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:41.18,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, this is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:43.80,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Come up with a plan \Nbefore she comes back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.20,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she's coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:48.77,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,She already finished checking! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:52.70,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, she stopped moving again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:59.18,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,P-Plug...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:00.14,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:03.94,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Now she's going back to \Nunplug the whole thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:06.15,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's one oversensitive ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:07.02,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Though I understand the feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:08.27,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:09.96,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,She can't come out of the TV if
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:11.87,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,she can't even make it \Noutside of the well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:14.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's been cursed by the kotatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:17.27,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she should just flip the breaker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:19.34,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:21.54,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,She's having trouble getting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.64,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,She brought the kotatsu with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:32.16,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,She was so worried that she \Nbrought the kotatsu out with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:34.74,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the wrong season \Nfor a kotatsu anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:36.53,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's not gonna happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:38.80,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,She can't bring that thing \Nout of the TV with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:40.49,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Our TV's too small!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:42.77,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It won't fit through!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:44.73,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You have to lead with the corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:48.10,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. I guess I'll give her a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:49.69,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no! Don't help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.53,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And how are you supposed \Nto get inside the TV?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:53.40,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for her though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:54.49,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,She's about to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:58.51,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, it doesn't seem like \Nyou'll be killing us,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:07:59.50,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,so could you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:01.71,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We'll play this Blu-ray \Nagain in a few days,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:03.88,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,so you can give it another shot then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:07.50,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:10.51,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,She's making herself comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:14.32,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,She's watching TV from inside the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:16.51,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,What's she trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.62,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me any crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:19.92,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:21.30,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This is our TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:24.33,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't scram, I'll Bubble \NFiction: Boom or Bust your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:26.27,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be off to a pretty crappy world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.82,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:31.93,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:36.24,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Could you spare one channel \Nfor me to spend the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:37.47,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Screw that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:40.05,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why should we let a ghost \Nuse one of our channels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:41.93,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You've got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:44.79,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a suspicious ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:47.36,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:09:01.10,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,See, I'm not a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:03.10,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.85,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:08.51,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:10.17,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,An imaginary angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:13.11,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Blu-wraith.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:15.31,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You're obviously not an angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:16.86,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You look the same as you did before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:19.33,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,More like you became an angel by
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:21.08,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,removing yourself from reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:23.12,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What's that thing hanging \Nfrom your neck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:28.25,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I can't leave the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:31.97,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,These defiled wings \Ncan't carry me anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:37.28,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I can only look up at the \Nsky from my rectangular box.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:39.12,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Blu-wraith is getting all blue on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:41.14,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,She's doing justice to her name!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:46.17,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I was created by a mad \Nscientist from another planet
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:49.63,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,as a program to place in \NBlu-rays for invading cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:55.17,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,When the Blu-ray is played, \NI become an electronic virus
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:57.31,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,that possesses every \Nsystem and destroys all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.31,0:09:58.82,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's not very angelic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:09:59.95,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'd call you a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:04.04,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,But before I could be played,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:06.91,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,the professor had to sell me to a \Nrecycle shop to pay off his debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:10.35,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since, I've been known \Nas the cursed Blu-ray
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:12.92,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and sent from planet to planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.14,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the cursed Blu-ray
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:18.49,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,because you curse appliances, \Nelectric devices?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.79,0:10:20.42,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:22.48,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I have nowhere else to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:24.28,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Let me stay in this TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:25.82,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,One channel is all I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:28.69,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Let me stay in this Braun tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:31.35,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This is all too sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:34.60,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you want to stay \Nin this cramped and dirty 1LDK?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:38.65,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,You could stay in a fancy 3D home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:44.07,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess you don't want a \Ndirty Blu-ray like me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:44.58,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:47.01,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.01,0:10:50.53,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's had their turn with me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:54.01,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,from recycle shop to recycle shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:56.75,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been abused by so many players.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:59.81,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody would want to play \Nthis slutty Blu-ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:01.83,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Should you really be
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:03.73,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,so blue about nobody \Nwanting to play you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:04.85,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,She's a Blu-ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:09.04,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I can no longer fly anywhere \Non these slutty wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:11.59,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make it to \Nchannel 5 or channel 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:15.34,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I belong on the dark Video 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:17.61,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,She just revealed that \Nshe wants to be on Video 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:21.13,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,If that is too much to ask for...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:23.62,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:26.19,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need these wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:29.62,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,After all, they broke long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.18,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe these wings will carry me away
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:34.63,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,if I make them bright red.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.62,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:37.50,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Video 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:38.94,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Video 1's what you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:40.01,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,What? Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:42.19,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Only until you find another home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:44.94,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And promise that you \Nwon't leave Video 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:47.51,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you. I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:49.87,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:50.93,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:56.47,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't be able to cry out of my right eye, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:58.11,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Very odd! Very red!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:59.74,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I want to show my appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.56,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,But I have nothing to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:03.61,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! It's okay, \Nso change channels!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:04.78,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let us control the TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.21,0:12:06.41,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:09.63,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to return the \Nfavor, so wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:10.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.71,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you flashing your right wing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:15.81,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,And please don't switch to Video 1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:17.68,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,before I've shown my appreciation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:18.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to give us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:19.72,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:21.58,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You only have one wing left!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:23.42,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:25.80,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I will never fly again,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:29.64,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,but my corpse can serve as a \Nlaunchpad to send you high up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:39.59,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san, is a color TV \Nsupposed to be so blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:41.82,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Video 1 is off-limits for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:44.15,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The transition to digital TV \Nis finished, so stick to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:45.73,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's watch something to cheer us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:47.48,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Is it time for Laugh Away?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:50.16,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Who's going to be on \NTelephone Shocking tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:52.66,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Blu-wraith
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.38,0:12:51.84,Main01,Tamo,0000,0000,0000,,Did you cut off your wing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:52.66,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:56.83,Main01,Tamo,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Did you cut your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:59.17,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san, I've never seen this \Nperson on Tamo-san Hour before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:59.17,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I cut off my wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:01.67,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Who brought her on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:04.15,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't Tamo-san saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:06.98,Main01,Tamo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we have flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:10.18,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on your appearance \Non Laugh Away?  - Blu-wraith
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:09.41,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And there's only one bouquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:10.71,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,From herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:13.20,Main01,Tamo,0000,0000,0000,,Introduce me to your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:16.49,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,No reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:18.44,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,This is as bad as when \NAkira Emoto was on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:20.13,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:22.69,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Stop making our TV blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:23.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:24.95,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Change channels!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:27.54,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Someone's making a run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:29.45,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's Right Wing! Right Wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:34.09,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well ma'am. I would consider \Nthat domestic violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:35.26,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:37.69,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted my husband to \Npay attention to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:39.21,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,So I snapped my wing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:44.21,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we'll be making angel \Nwingtip with blue cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:47.86,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's the same color!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:50.73,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,A very black blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.99,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty thousand, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:07.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps, you're part of the \Nmake-me-blue movement?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:08.60,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:09.70,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Drop a zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:12.54,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,That zero might save your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.54,0:14:14.20,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,You want this to blow up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:14.95,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:19.76,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Still, you're an oddball.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:22.21,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you put a GPS on a scooter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:26.22,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,With a Blu-ray player to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:28.89,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at a crossroads in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:30.65,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,A very blue crossroads.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:33.51,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let that Blu-ray player \Nget you into an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:40.37,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I moved you over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:43.00,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:45.40,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You better earn me the 50 grand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:50.60,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry about causing \Nyou so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:52.72,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't fit on a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:55.59,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,video tape because I was \Nsupposed to be capable
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.59,0:14:57.43,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,of destroying entire cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.27,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:01.47,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I will hang myself in apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:02.79,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, you already hanged yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:04.13,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:06.57,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No more hanging or wing snapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:08.79,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna pay me back \Nby serving as my navigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:11.80,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,A fool like you should still \Nbe able to read a map, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:13.76,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:18.45,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,You have set me free from my cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:22.31,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're like my wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:25.52,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I-In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:28.61,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer need this defiled wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:31.11,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! I told you to stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.46,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You really want to rip your wings off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:35.40,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Take better care of your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:38.68,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I feel better when I see blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:42.37,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,because I may feel blue. \NBut my blood is still red.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:43.49,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we have our destination!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:44.75,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me the way to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:48.76,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on a delivery, so do a proper job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:50.99,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This is where we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:51.98,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Bring up the map!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:53.89,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,U-Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:58.87,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,The blue wing is our current location.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:16:01.01,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination is the red wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:02.90,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The whole screen is covered in red!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.90,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Who said anything about blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:09.09,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I wanted to help you \Ncalm down and drive safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:10.34,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,How is this supposed to calm me down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:12.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell where I'm \Ngoing with all this blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:16.33,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You should give me a more \Nrealistic demonstration!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.79,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:21.53,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:23.01,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:26.25,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And tell me stuff like how many \Nmeters many until a turn to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:29.81,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Turn right in 25 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:36.19,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Turn right in 50 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:40.27,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Turn right in 75 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:44.50,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, why do I keep turning right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:46.29,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back where I started?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:47.41,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:50.53,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:54.98,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,But I only have a right wing to turn....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:56.28,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody said to turn your wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:58.53,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:03.05,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,It will be another 125 meters \Nbefore I can snap the next bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:05.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody wants to hear about \Nyour broken angel wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:07.41,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Give me my damn directions!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:09.58,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:15.05,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody cares about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:16.82,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Turn left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.23,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.96,0:17:20.30,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Continue forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:24.69,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:26.67,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:30.44,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,If nobody cares about my \Nlife, I'm already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.65,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:33.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This navigation system \Nis a pain the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:35.56,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:37.64,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,My navigation is too heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:40.69,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I am nothing but a chain on your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:41.78,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:43.08,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.46,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The hell are you on?! I'm riding \Non the scooter you're in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:47.20,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:49.65,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,When this job is finished, \NI'll listen to your story!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:51.25,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Just give me directions right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:53.28,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on navigating!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:55.17,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:56.22,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:18:00.18,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Turn right in 150 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:03.23,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. Excellent. \NThat's more like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:06.69,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Turn left in 20 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:09.08,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,You are too close to the \Ncar in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:12.32,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're pretty good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:15.11,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So turn right, turn left... What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:18.15,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Kotatsu six kilometers behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:19.70,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What does your kotatsu \Nhave to do with anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:20.81,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to turn around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:22.70,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You need to go check \Nif it's turned off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.72,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep worrying \Nabout your kotatsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:27.11,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,You are too far away from the kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:29.74,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Current distance: 6,238 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:32.04,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares how far away the kotatsu is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:35.92,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Distance between our \Nhearts: 6,343 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:38.71,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,How does that even make sense?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:40.78,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Where is your heart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:43.74,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,So close...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:46.18,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,And yet so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:48.63,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,You are so far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:50.39,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This navigation system \Nis a pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:53.73,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you're straight out \Nof a Shinji Nojima serial!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.31,0:18:59.86,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding! You're \Nnot a pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:01.36,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the concern!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:04.24,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry, you \Nturned off the kotatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:06.29,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:07.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Do your job, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:09.96,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:11.98,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop worrying \Nabout the kotatsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:15.00,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure? Are you really sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:17.26,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! Stop worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.29,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:21.55,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I had a traumatic experience \Ninvolving a kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:24.47,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, could you just do your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:25.41,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:29.77,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for him that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:31.56,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:33.02,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're like those couples who \Nget stuck in a traffic jam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:34.61,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,and start watching shows \Non their navigation system!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:39.82,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,My boyfriend was so possessive that \Nhe wouldn't let me go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.10,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Boyfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:43.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the mad \Nscientist who made you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:46.38,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And is this like a flashback \Nin a flashback?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:48.58,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,When I tried to go outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:52.79,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,he would use d-doner kebab.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:54.36,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Domestic violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:55.79,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You were completely off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:57.67,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And did he just rip off a wing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:19:59.09,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You had two earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:02.26,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I had six wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:03.13,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:06.10,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And how come you can talk straight now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:10.10,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to convince myself that \Nhe was acting out of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:13.10,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,But there was one thing that worried me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:18.89,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,My mad boyfriend would always leave me and go away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:21.11,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:23.45,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,He went to Fukuoka a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.03,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Last week, it was Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:26.61,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Today, he went to Nagoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:29.39,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Are these really business trips?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:33.25,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Or is he going to see other women?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.61,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuoka, Hokkaido, and Nagoya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:36.88,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you from a different planet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:39.54,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I could only sit under a kotatsu and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:41.70,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,watch reruns of Shinji \NNojima serials while
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:42.93,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,waiting for him to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:44.20,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:46.39,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it have to be Shinji Nojima?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:50.02,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,Then I woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:53.32,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,I could smell something delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:57.27,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,It was a gift from Nagoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:59.78,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,My boyfriend was really \Non a business trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:03.09,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,And he bought a present for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:09.52,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,But then I realized that \Nit wasn't a present from Nagoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:14.29,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,It was my wing that had been burned \Nby the heat from the kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:16.29,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:28.55,Main01,Ghost,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I was traumatized by \Nkotatsu, wings, and Shinji Nojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:30.37,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:32.97,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody has to deal \Nwith their own pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:36.10,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who cares if you \Ndon't have any wings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:38.02,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need any wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:42.07,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you where you want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:44.65,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:57.46,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, the sky is so blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:34.93,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode: So in the Second Season of Prison Break,\N They're Already Broken Out of Prison,\N But the Name Works Once You Realize That Society is a Prison
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.70,0:23:32.53,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:34.93,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm innocent!
